---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Terms of Service | Apex Corporate Solutions'>
    <section class='py-20 bg-background'>
        <div class='container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 max-w-3xl'>
            <h1 class='text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2'>
                Standard Terms and Conditions of Service
            </h1>
            <p class='text-muted-foreground mb-8'>
                Last Updated: 21 November 2025
            </p>

            <div
                class='prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8'
            >
                <p>
                    These Terms and Conditions ("Terms") govern the provision of
                    digital infrastructure, hosting, and design services by Apex
                    Corporate Solutions, a trading division of Playhouse Media
                    Group (Pty) Ltd ("The Provider"), to the entity or
                    individual subscribing to these services ("The Client"). By
                    paying the Activation Fee or subscribing to a monthly
                    package, the Client accepts these Terms in full.
                </p>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        1. SERVICE SUBSCRIPTION & PAYMENT
                    </h2>
                    <ul class='list-none space-y-4 pl-0'>
                        <li>
                            <strong>1.1. Activation Fee:</strong> All services require
                            a once-off Activation Fee to cover design and setup costs.
                            Work will not commence until this fee is paid in full.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>1.2. Monthly Subscriptions:</strong>
                            <ul class='list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1'>
                                <li>
                                    Service fees are billed monthly in advance.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Invoices are generated on the 25th of each
                                    month.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Payment is strictly due on the 1st day of
                                    the calendar month.
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>1.3. Payment Method:</strong> The Client agrees
                            to pay via automated Recurring Billing (Debit Order/Card
                            Authority) or Electronic Funds Transfer (EFT) before
                            the due date.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>1.4. Non-Payment & Suspension:</strong>
                            <ul class='list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1'>
                                <li>
                                    A grace period of 3 (three) days is allowed.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    If payment is not received by the 4th of the
                                    month, all services (including Email,
                                    Website, and Hosting) will be automatically
                                    suspended.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    A Reactivation Fee of R150.00 will be
                                    charged to restore suspended services.
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>1.5. Price Adjustments:</strong> The Provider
                            reserves the right to adjust monthly fees annually to
                            account for inflation and supplier cost increases. Clients
                            will receive 30 days' written notice of any price change.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        2. HOSTING & DOMAINS
                    </h2>
                    <ul class='list-none space-y-4 pl-0'>
                        <li>
                            <strong>2.1. Reseller Status:</strong> The Provider acts
                            as a reseller for upstream hosting providers (e.g., HostAfrica).
                            While we strive for 99.9% uptime, we cannot guarantee
                            uninterrupted service due to upstream network failures.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>2.2. Domain Ownership:</strong> The domain name
                            registered (e.g., yourcompany.co.za) remains the property
                            of the Client, provided the account is in good standing.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>2.3. Domain Renewal:</strong> If the Client cancels
                            services or fails to pay, the domain name may expire.
                            The Provider is not liable for the loss of a domain name
                            due to non-payment.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>2.4. Data Retention:</strong> If an account remains
                            unpaid for 60 days, the Provider reserves the right to
                            permanently delete all data (emails and website files)
                            from the server to recover storage space.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        3. DESIGN SERVICES (WEB & BRANDING)
                    </h2>
                    <ul class='list-none space-y-4 pl-0'>
                        <li>
                            <strong>3.1. Scope:</strong> The Activation Fee includes
                            the design of digital assets as specified in the chosen
                            package (e.g., Logo, Letterhead, Website).
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>3.2. Revisions:</strong> To ensure timely delivery,
                            design services include a maximum of 2 (two) rounds of
                            revisions. Additional changes requested by the Client
                            will be billed at the Provider’s standard hourly rate
                            (R450/hour).
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>3.3. Content Supply:</strong> The Client is responsible
                            for supplying all text, images, and logo files required
                            for the website or profile. Delays in supplying content
                            will not pause the billing of the monthly subscription.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>3.4. Approval:</strong> Once the Client approves
                            a design (via email or WhatsApp), any subsequent changes
                            are billable.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        4. CANCELLATION & TERMINATION
                    </h2>
                    <ul class='list-none space-y-4 pl-0'>
                        <li>
                            <strong>4.1. Notice Period:</strong> This is a month-to-month
                            agreement. The Client may cancel services at any time
                            by providing 30 calendar days' written notice via email
                            to <a
                                href='mailto:jacob@apexcorporate.co.za'
                                class='text-primary hover:underline'
                                >jacob@apexcorporate.co.za</a
                            >.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>4.2. Transfer:</strong> Upon valid cancellation
                            (and provided all fees are paid), the Provider will issue
                            a Domain Transfer Ticket to the Client’s new service
                            provider free of charge.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        5. LIMITATION OF LIABILITY
                    </h2>
                    <ul class='list-none space-y-4 pl-0'>
                        <li>
                            <strong>5.1. Data Loss:</strong> While the Provider performs
                            automated backups (on specific packages), the Client
                            is ultimately responsible for their own data. The Provider
                            is not liable for data loss caused by server failure,
                            hacking, or human error.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>5.2. Business Operations:</strong> The Provider
                            is not liable for any loss of revenue, loss of tenders,
                            or business interruption caused by email downtime or
                            website unavailability.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>5.3. Compliance:</strong> While we assist with
                            structure and design, the accuracy of the content in
                            Company Profiles and Tender Documents is the sole responsibility
                            of the Client.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>6. GENERAL</h2>
                    <ul class='list-none space-y-4 pl-0'>
                        <li>
                            <strong>6.1. Jurisdiction:</strong> These Terms are governed
