                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>6.2. Severability:</strong> If any part of these
                            Terms is found to be invalid, the remaining sections
                            shall remain in full force and effect.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
